{"tid":870462,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"D女到底諗緊乜? 求解答","createTime":"2018-10-21T06:55:33.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-22T03:48:13.000Z","uid":82384,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"d384594dcd6cf25eac2e3ab98b5d6ba6a810942c","tid":870462,"uid":82384,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-21T06:55:33.000Z","msg":"你話我因為掛住返工/打機唔理佢，係唔尊重佢，我無所謂，係我錯，我係忽略左你&hellip;<br />\n但你暪住我同成班男人去旅行又點計？<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/green_cap_3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咁你又有冇尊重我？重好意思話我控制你太多，問你同邊個去都唔得？ 重想周圍收兵，而加重主動話我對你差要分手？<br />\n你諗緊咩呀八婆？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7ab9a9a36df3141c226b8d99f84cf8563fb2f31","tid":870462,"uid":1249,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-21T06:56:32.000Z","msg":"冷靜D照下鏡, 睇下自己個樣, 同埋睇下你本銀行存摺有幾多錢先啦<br />\n<br />\n世界好公平<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n如果人人都心想事成<br />\n<br />\n會天下大亂<br />\n<br />\n世上總要有你D咁既廢人"},{"pid":"b9828b29e8e952a8bbd277c8801be1349bd081b3","tid":870462,"uid":38405,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-21T06:57:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/green_cap_3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/green_cap_3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3017a96df81e5f1a1908a5e8a5bb67fea1f53dc","tid":870462,"uid":108236,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-21T06:58:15.000Z","msg":"樣子 性格 錢 你有齊3樣 最後佢都係會同係你一齊<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 中間大家各自搵下sp咪算<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6df214c7bb81b92299ec84051b13a752f93ebe36","tid":870462,"uid":179967,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-21T06:59:03.000Z","msg":"好明顯搵藉口同你分手 已經有第2個<br />\n醒下啦"},{"pid":"12293b50c1915664e6a3a7175e7a2ffe30d0bff0","tid":870462,"uid":179990,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-21T07:07:05.000Z","msg":"你條女: 「就係因為你成日打機無時間陪我<b